1. Add a task: Use addTask to add tasks to the schedule. Example:
Task task = factory.createTask("Task Description", "HH:MM", "HH:MM", "Priority");
manager.addTask(task);

2.Remove a task: Use removeTask to remove a task by its description. Example:
manager.removeTask("Task Description");

3. Edit a task: Use editTask to modify an existing task's details. Example:
manager.editTask("Old Description", "New Description", "HH:MM", "HH:MM", "Priority");

4. Mark task as completed: Example:
manager.markTaskCompleted("Task Description");

5. View tasks by priority: Example:
manager.viewTasksByPriority("Priority Level");
